name: MascotGenerator
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: mascot generator
des:
Mascots are resources that have been used by amateur and professional sports teams, and now you can have your own! Just answer a few yes/no questions, and Alexa will generate one that can be used as your identity in fitness apps, or to wear on the bib for a big race. When getting tired in training, just think of the mascot being there to cheer you on!

Get started, and Alexa will choose from over twenty different questions to personalize your mascot that suits your tastes. Let's get started!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
